evil will befall you, because you will do what is evil in the sight of the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>, provoking him to anger through the work of your hands.\u201d</span></p>\n<h3 class=\"s1\">The Song of Moses</h3>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"v5_31_30\"><sup id=\"Deut.31.30\" class=\"v5_31_30\">30</sup>Then Moses spoke the words of this song until they were finished, in the ears of all the assembly of Israel:</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n</div>\n", 
